==English==

===Noun===
'''[[hyperbolic]] [[sine]]'''

#{{mathematics}} A [[hyperbolic function]] that is written in symbol ''[[sinh]]'' and defined as
:<math>\sinh(x) = \frac{e^x - e^{-x}}{2}</math>

====Translations====
*German: [[Sinus hyperbolicus]] {{m}}
*Japanese: [[ハイパボリックサイン]] (haipaborikku sain), [[双曲正弦]] (sōkyoku seigen)
*Swedish: [[sinus hyperbolicus]] {{c}}
